{"tid":856264,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦新手想問發生咩事","createTime":"2018-10-10T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T09:46:14.000Z","uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0b79d9e5547583e46f5c93cddeb92c5db4f69e","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"我部電腦前排壞左 咁見佢有補養就拎返去佢間野維修，咁等左個半月終於拎得返部機啦 。原本諗住開開心心打鋪機 點知開左隻game幾分鐘就卡屏 ，跟住個幾秒仲自動熄埋機。咁我以為唔好彩啫 開多次之後又係咁，之後仲要開唔返部機。同部電腦拎去維修之前個種壞法又有幾分相似。但係維修個邊又話幫我換左粒cpu 應該冇問題，真係冇晒辦法 所以想請教一下大家電腦發生咩事。"},{"pid":"c8e34ce07f50a5835db8626eeca23173960dd5cf","tid":856264,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"有幾何會壞cpu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7022f8dd3f1e44e077026138abaef136f68737bf","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8e34ce07f50a5835db8626eeca23173960dd5cf","tid":856264,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"有幾何會壞cpu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"本身好似散熱唔好 所以今日專登換左好多散熱既野  估唔到又係咁。"},{"pid":"04f9b3ad711f67b2cc9139d6a7dd514f0072d70d","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"e73a29f806fd99d2af525045e53e183f9b025049","tid":856264,"uid":171917,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"本身用緊咩 廠機？<br />\n換左咩I?<br />\nAs this always list please!"},{"pid":"9dca16eb9826577456e3f1892dbe3ec47997b642","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"e73a29f806fd99d2af525045e53e183f9b025049","tid":856264,"uid":171917,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"本身用緊咩 廠機？<br />\n換左咩I?<br />\nAs this always list please!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"唔係廠機。<br />\n佢話換左另一粒同型號既cpu。<br />\ncpu:  amd ryzen 5 1600<br />\n顯卡: gigabyte geforce gtx 1070<br />\nram: g.skill ddr4 3000mhz 8gb x2 <br />\n火牛: antec 550w 80plus bronze<br />\n低板: asrock ab350m pro4 b350<br />\n<br />\n我電腦方面真係唔叻 所以好大機會比人水，但係只求安安樂樂打鋪機。。有錯既地方希望可以屌細力d。"},{"pid":"b9b0a4073ea1267448de8cf75b238864f441114e","tid":856264,"uid":37107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"換左粒cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2034093350778cc9d9992ad22816ee736412a420","tid":856264,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"比人昆左"},{"pid":"ba48fe97380e7f7d4f887247d1954bbd186b5de3","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2034093350778cc9d9992ad22816ee736412a420","tid":856264,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"比人昆左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"唔該先，但想知比人昆個部份係?"},{"pid":"90b34554795e7997a81a975925e35e0771bd623c","tid":856264,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"應該唔關cpu事"},{"pid":"310b763f00576023dff58088dc8beeaed03df7c0","tid":856264,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"通常係火牛或者硬盤出事，自動關機好多原因答你唔到，搵個好啲既商戶幫你全部檢查咪知乜事"},{"pid":"e859551ac1328193923be860ca6ea3279e542892","tid":856264,"uid":200407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310b763f00576023dff58088dc8beeaed03df7c0","tid":856264,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"通常係火牛或者硬盤出事，自動關機好多原因答你唔到，搵個好啲既商戶幫你全部檢查咪知乜事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"知道，但想再聽多幾位巴打既睇法先，不過都唔該晒你。"},{"pid":"a51ae77de07d3dfdb39daf8ff3cbeccfe62fabde","tid":856264,"uid":171917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi